title: X-men - Not in Continuity [July 2014]
description:
I'm seeding this for today, then I'm moving it into my archive. As soon as this has enough seeds I'll upload part 2.



These are not my torrents, but I salvaged them from limbo a few days ago on another site and there's been too many hit and runs since then--and I just don't have the bandwidth to be treated as a dedicated download for this collection. So grab this while the grabbing is good.
